In [33]:
df['unit_int']=df.unit.str.extract(r'(\d*)')
df['unit_int']=pd.to_numeric(df.unit_int,errors='ignore')
df['unit_str']='(1'+df.unit.str.extract(r"([가-힣a-zA-Z]+)")+'당)'
df['avg']=df.price/df.unit_int
df

In [35]:
result=np.array([])
for i in range(len(df)):
    if df['unit_str'].iloc[i]=="(1kg당)":
        result=np.append(result,df['avg'].iloc[i]/1000)
    else:
        result=np.append(result,df['avg'].iloc[i])
result

foodKinds={"grain":[],"vegetable":[],"fruit":[],"protein":[],"dairy":[]}

    foodKinds[df.loc[i,"type"]].append(df.loc[i,"name"])

result1=[]
for i in range(len(foodKinds_product)):
    foodType=foodKinds_product[i]
    total_cost=0
    for food,amount in zip(foodType,list(current_per.values())):
        cost=foodCost.loc[food,"cost_per"]
        total_cost+=cost*amount
    result1.append(total_cost)
